{"tid":270123,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"13年利迷有感而發","createTime":"2017-06-04T06:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T11:34:56.000Z","uid":121045,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87534396a39358f799fcbf5a3ab3a6e99464660b","tid":270123,"uid":121045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"我真係寧願好似利物浦咁熱血足球都唔想好似賤種蝗咁雙冠皇<br />\n<br />\n1. 熱血高普 高普就連和西布朗都會帶領球隊向球迷致謝 熱血慶祝 屌你垃圾施丹 贏歐聯都木口木面好似死老豆咁 做咩姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/143306_4d1c2e6d6b6a45e77f87a463b3d529f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F143306_4d1c2e6d6b6a45e77f87a463b3d529f3.jpg&h=e6a8555f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 對頭六球隊未嘗一敗 我敢寫包單就算賤種黎英超呀 都唔可以對頭六不敗呀 如果唔係文尼重傷 一定係今季英超冠軍 唔似得有啲隊咁洗左億幾都排第六 要靠歐霸先有得打歐聯<br />\n<br />\n3. 用人渣士隊波都可以踢出漂亮足球 試問英超有邊隊踢法可以靚過利物浦？車路士都比唔上喇 去到大直路果時基本上場場都係-6既 曼市兩隊垃圾唔講 阿仙奴就靠黑哨 -6波都冇頭四 熱狗就矛閪<br />\n<br />\n4. 重返歐洲場賽 唔好唔記得利物浦始終係英格蘭贏得最多歐聯既球隊 前幾年只係一時失手姐 我永遠都會記得09年我地大炒賤種4-0既畫面 07作客贏巴狗比拿美入波打golf慶祝 賤種下年歐聯再一決高下喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/143404_a9e8ce7d2854b0aa150ae92e3a8ae664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F143404_a9e8ce7d2854b0aa150ae92e3a8ae664.jpg&h=f9331155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8166e1ed8c0e5182233bedb932aa42d8f205f791","tid":270123,"uid":121045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/143529_c51bd3fe893643a905586c7073ee4d39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F143529_c51bd3fe893643a905586c7073ee4d39.jpg&h=0284c29a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/143541_d79af3177bbfc334df5bd653c821873d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%